ref_solution:
We can determine the distance from $O$ to $P$ by dropping a perpendicular from $P$ to $T$ on the $x$-axis. [asy]
unitsize(0.2 cm);
defaultpen(linewidth(.7pt)+fontsize(10pt));
dotfactor=4;
draw(Circle((0,0),7)); draw(Circle((0,0),10));
